<div class="mb-requirement-container">
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16078">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> </span>
      <b>NOTE: </b> The official merit badge pamphlets are now free and
      downloadable
      <a
        href="https://filestore.scouting.org/filestore/Merit_Badge_ReqandRes/Pamphlets/Veterinary%20Medicine.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        >HERE</a
      >
      or can be purchased at the
      <a href="https://www.scoutshop.org/" target="_blank ">Scout Shop.</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16079">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 1. </span>
      Discuss with your counselor the roles a veterinarian plays in the
      following:
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16079 mb-requirement-id-16080">
        (a) Companion or small animal medicine, and equine medicine <br /><i
          >Resources:</i
        >
        <a href="https://youtu.be/BCnueH9iemg" target="_blank"
          >Equine Veterinarian | Future Jobs L Explore a Career as a Horse
          Doctor (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://youtu.be/5XrzUiCLw3A" target="_blank"
          >A Day in the Life of a Vet | If You See It, You Can Be It (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16079 mb-requirement-id-16081">
        (b) Food animal or large animal medicine <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/bUCUCgVStB8" target="_blank"
          >Working the Land: Large Animal Veterinarian (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://youtu.be/QGGDyQj8rx0" target="_blank"
          >Cattle Caretakers: Large Animal Veterinarian (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16079 mb-requirement-id-16082">
        (c) Exotic animal medicine <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a
          href="https://www.dvm360.com/view/caring-for-exotic-animals"
          target="_blank"
          >Caring for Exotic Animals (website/video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://youtu.be/H9Q7ItFXH3c" target="_blank"
          >A Day in the Life of an Exotic Bird Veterinarian (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16079 mb-requirement-id-16083">
        (d) Marine animal medicine (mammal and fish) <br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/SK6DcOaxaz0" target="_blank"
          >Why Science? Marine Animal Veterinarian (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16079 mb-requirement-id-16084">
        (e) Poultry medicine <br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/GdQgnsoZf-U" target="_blank"
          >VetsOnCall - Us Chicken Farms Are Humane + Family-Run, Vets Show
          (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16079 mb-requirement-id-16085">
        (f) Wildlife medicine and aquaculture medicine <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/UzxMrfHOEE0" target="_blank"
          >A Career in Aquatic Animal Medicine (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://youtu.be/C4g2v08D2gY" target="_blank"
          >How Does a Wildlife Veterinarian Do It?! (video)</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #515354"></div>
    <br />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16086">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 2. </span>
      Discuss with your counselor the roles a veterinarian plays in the
      following:
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16086 mb-requirement-id-16087">
        (a) Public health medicine and zoonotic disease surveillance and control
        <br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/OeZDZofWjl4" target="_blank"
          >Career Connections: Public Health Veterinarian (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16086 mb-requirement-id-16088">
        (b) The military <br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/NsGMXjfnHXQ" target="_blank"
          >Cool Jobs: Army Veterinarian (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16086 mb-requirement-id-16089">
        (c) Food safety and inspection <br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/PUq9PjfmCJw" target="_blank"
          >USFDA Public Health Veterinarian (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16086 mb-requirement-id-16090">
        (d) Laboratory animal medicine and research <br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/iqZ_JhXAFnQ" target="_blank"
          >Laboratory Animal Veterinarian (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16086 mb-requirement-id-16091">
        (e) Teaching and government <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a
          href="https://jobs.wsma.org/career/veterinary-medicine-teacher"
          target="_blank"
          >Veterinary Medicine Teacher Overview (website)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://youtu.be/cwohn5eJsnU" target="_blank"
          >Veterinarian for Working Dogs - Government (video)</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #515354"></div>
    <br />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16095">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 3. </span>
      Describe the training required to become a veterinarian. Where is the
      veterinary medical college in your state or nearest to you? Describe the
      prerequisites for applying to veterinary school.<br /><i>Resources:</i>
      <a href="https://youtu.be/nzIUfwonJlk" target="_blank"
        >How Long Does It Take to Become a Veterinarian and Board Certified?
        (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a
        href="https://www.avma.org/education/center-for-veterinary-accreditation/accredited-veterinary-colleges"
        target="_blank"
        >Accredited Veterinary Colleges (website)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16096">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 4. </span>
      Tell your counselor what a registered veterinary technician (R.V.T.) or
      animal health technician (A.H.T.) is. Describe the training required to
      become an R.V.T. or A.H.T. Where is the school or facility for R.V.T. or
      A.H.T training in your state or nearest to you? Describe the role an
      R.V.T. or A.H.T. would play in assisting a veterinarian working in three
      of the practice types listed in requirement 1. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
      <a href="https://youtu.be/7dNnOGMxiLs" target="_blank"
        >What Is an RVT? (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a href="https://youtu.be/UFkLQmM3Aew" target="_blank"
        >How To Become a Registered Veterinary Technician (RVT) (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a href="https://youtu.be/qu-lmIlWJfE" target="_blank"
        >Registered Animal Health Technician (video)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16097">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 5. </span>
      Discuss with your counselor the role a veterinarian plays in the
      human-animal bond. <br /><i>Resource:</i>
      <a href="https://youtu.be/7tVGEzh-JHs" target="_blank"
        >The Center for the Human-Animal Bond (video)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16092">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 6. </span>
      Do ONE of the following:
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16092 mb-requirement-id-16093">
        (a) Visit a veterinary clinic, hospital, or veterinary referral teaching
        hospital that does work in one of the practices listed in requirement 1.
        Spend as much time as you can observing the veterinarians and their
        staff. Prepare a presentation on what you observed and learned at the
        facility and share with your counselor.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16092 mb-requirement-id-16094">
        (b) Spend as much time as possible with a veterinarian who works in one
        of the fields listed in requirement 2. Learn what special training
        beyond veterinary medical school may have been required for that
        position. Learn about any special or unusual activities required of this
        position. Prepare a presentation and share what you have learned about
        this field of veterinary medicine with your counselor. Include how this
        field serves the needs of the general public.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #515354"></div>
    <br />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-16098">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 7. </span>
      Select one career from any of the lists in requirements 1 or 2. Discuss
      the following with your counselor: <i>Resources:</i>
      <a href="https://youtu.be/DHdVl3OV_YY" target="_blank"
        >How To Become a Veterinarian (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a href="https://youtu.be/dAISdyqNHlo" target="_blank"
        >The Many Career Paths in Veterinary Medicine (video)</a
      >
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16098 mb-requirement-id-16099">
        (a) Why would one choose this particular career field?
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16098 mb-requirement-id-16100">
        (b) What would you like about this job?
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16098 mb-requirement-id-16101">
        (c) What would be the biggest challenges in doing this job?
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16098 mb-requirement-id-16102">
        (d) What to you has been the most surprising aspect of this job?
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-16098 mb-requirement-id-16103">
        (e) What continuing education requirements are required to maintain
        certification for this job?
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #515354"></div>
    <br />
  </div>
</div>
